##### Automated Installation _(Using [Yuyi](https://github.com/brewster1134/Yuyi))_

_create a `menu.yml` in `~/Documents` with the following_
```yaml
ruby:
  versions: ['<%= RUBY_VERSION %>']
bundler:
node:
npm:
testem:
phantom_js:
# growl:
```
_and then run_

`ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/brewster1134/Yuyi/master/bin/install)"`

##### Manual Installation _\* may be incomplete_

```shell
ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/Homebrew/homebrew/go/install)"
brew install rbenv
brew install ruby-build
brew install node
brew install phantomjs
rbenv install <%= RUBY_VERSION %>
gem update --system
gem install bundler
bundle install
npm install testem -g
```

### Compiling
`bundle exec guard`

Do **NOT** modify any `.js` files!  Modify the coffee files in the `src` directory.  Guard will watch for changes and compile them to the `lib` directory.

### Testing
Run `testem`

_- or -_

Run `testem -g` if running OS X Lion or below for Growl support

